# Game Mechanics Implementation Guide

## Text Fading System
- Non-keyword text should gradually fade out over time
- Use opacity animations with configurable duration
- Implement random selection for which words fade first

## Keyword Highlighting
- Keywords should glow using the `accent-blue` color
- Implement pulsing animation for keywords
- Saved keywords should be highlighted permanently with `accent-blue`

## Timer System
- Use a linear progress indicator for the timer
- Change color to `danger-red` when time is running low (< 20%)
- Timer should be pausable and resumable

## Scoring System
- 3-star rating: All keywords saved
- 2-star rating: More than minimum keywords saved
- 1-star rating: Minimum required keywords saved
- 0-star rating: Failed to save minimum keywords

Always ensure game mechanics are implemented consistently across all chapters.